00:01:26.044 --> 00:01:29.839 position:50% align:center
There's a lot of blood, but I didn't
get a concussion. Don't worry.

00:01:29.839 --> 00:01:33.426 position:50% align:center
I wouldn't get worried after all this time.

00:01:33.426 --> 00:01:35.178 position:50% align:center
Really?

00:01:35.178 --> 00:01:38.348 position:50% align:center
You're shaking. You <i>tsundere</i>.

00:01:38.348 --> 00:01:41.267 position:50% align:center
