00:01:41.267 --> 00:01:45.146 position:50% align:center
Natsusa, didn't you cry when I got hurt, too?

00:01:45.146 --> 00:01:46.648 position:50% align:center
--I didn't cry!
--Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!

00:01:46.648 --> 00:01:49.192 position:50% align:center
--Huh? Really?
--Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!

00:01:49.192 --> 00:01:50.902 position:50% align:center
You're pulling the skin on my wound!

00:01:50.902 --> 00:01:52.946 position:50% align:center
It's your fault for saying unnecessary things!

00:01:52.946 --> 00:01:54.572 position:50% align:center
