to take care of something like this!

00:01:55.573 --> 00:01:58.660 position:50% align:center
"20 Makoto Someya"
--Spit?! Is your spit some kind of panacea?!
--A little spit would be enough
to take care of something like this!

00:01:58.660 --> 00:02:00.954 position:50% align:center
