00:02:00.954 --> 00:02:02.163 position:50% align:center
Shit!

00:02:02.163 --> 00:02:06.376 position:50% align:center
It's only been a few weeks,
but I feel so nervous!

00:02:06.376 --> 00:02:07.919 position:50% align:center
Makoto.

00:02:07.919 --> 00:02:12.424 position:50% align:center
You probably already know,
but be careful of their number 8.

00:02:12.424 --> 00:02:14.384 position:50% align:center
I'll give you my complete support.

00:02:16.428 --> 00:02:17.595 position:50% align:center
Yeah.

00:02:20.557 --> 00:02:22.976 position:50% align:center
I'll protect Mako-<i>san</i>.

00:02:27.439 --> 00:02:28.440 position:50% align:center
Hey!

00:02:31.860 --> 00:02:32.861 position:50% align:center
Here he comes!

00:02:57.469 --> 00:02:59.137 position:50% align:center
Failure to release the ball.

00:03:00.597 --> 00:03:03.767 position:50% align:center
I wanted to copy that play style of yours.

00:03:03.767 --> 00:03:06.269 position:50% align:center
As expected of Natsu-<i>san</i>'s senior.

00:03:06.269 --> 00:03:08.897 position:50% align:center
What a terrible personality...

00:03:08.897 --> 00:03:11.941 position:50% align:center
Like I thought, he's a really tough opponent.

00:03:15.320 --> 00:03:18.656 position:50% align:center
They got a penalty on us at a bad time...

00:03:23.203 --> 00:03:24.204 position:50% align:center
Makoto.

00:03:24.204 --> 00:03:28.958 position:50% align:center
Be careful. Keep passing to the backs,
and we'll manage somehow.

00:03:28.958 --> 00:03:30.126 position:50% align:center
Got it...

00:03:36.424 --> 00:03:42.180 position:50% align:center
The moment Mako-<i>san </i>entered the field,
he went back to his old position...

00:03:49.813 --> 00:03:54.484 position:50% align:center
Uchinashi. Uchinashi!

00:03:54.484 --> 00:03:57.195 position:50% align:center
Join. Hurry.

00:04:00.865 --> 00:04:02.450 position:50% align:center
I see.

00:04:02.450 --> 00:04:07.872 position:50% align:center
Ueoka is a threat, but I'm not...

00:04:09.582 --> 00:04:11.710 position:50% align:center
Thank goodness.

00:04:11.710 --> 00:04:12.961 position:50% align:center
Nervousness?

00:04:12.961 --> 00:04:14.504 position:50% align:center
How stupid.

00:04:14.504 --> 00:04:18.008 position:50% align:center
No point in feeling nervous after
being looked down on so blatantly.

00:04:18.008 --> 00:04:19.968 position:50% align:center
Thanks to him, I remember now.

00:04:19.968 --> 00:04:21.344 position:50% align:center
Crouch!

00:04:21.344 --> 00:04:22.345 position:50% align:center
Bind!

00:04:22.345 --> 00:04:23.471 position:50% align:center
Set!

00:04:26.141 --> 00:04:27.934 position:50% align:center
Push 'em down!

00:04:31.563 --> 00:04:33.064 position:50% align:center
That's not enough!

00:04:41.239 --> 00:04:42.282 position:50% align:center
We did it!

00:04:44.075 --> 00:04:47.162 position:50% align:center
I had forgotten.

00:04:47.162 --> 00:04:49.080 position:50% align:center
For a long time now...

00:04:51.875 --> 00:04:53.918 position:50% align:center
We'll kill you if you look down on us.

00:04:53.918 --> 00:04:55.545 position:50% align:center
Ikuto!

00:05:00.925 --> 00:05:02.302 position:50% align:center
Shit! What should I do?!

00:05:02.302 --> 00:05:03.803 position:50% align:center
This is it!

00:05:03.803 --> 00:05:06.890 position:50% align:center
The best part of rugby!

00:05:12.103 --> 00:05:16.107 position:50% align:center
Huh? Isn't this a bit tough?

00:05:16.107 --> 00:05:18.151 position:50% align:center
That's not enough!

00:05:18.151 --> 00:05:20.320 position:50% align:center
Way too tough!

00:05:29.621 --> 00:05:31.664 position:50% align:center
I had forgotten.

00:05:31.664 --> 00:05:35.960 position:50% align:center
The expectations of my high school
and the pressure from my juniors...

00:05:35.960 --> 00:05:40.423 position:50% align:center
I was caught up with all of that
and let myself falter.

00:05:40.423 --> 00:05:43.093 position:50% align:center
This fighting spirit that
makes you lose your mind...

00:05:44.427 --> 00:05:46.137 position:50% align:center
Try!

00:05:46.137 --> 00:05:50.058 position:50% align:center
...and the rush that wraps
around you when you score a try...

00:05:52.185 --> 00:05:55.814 position:50% align:center
I had forgotten it all for so long.

00:05:55.814 --> 00:05:58.191 position:50% align:center
That felt so good!

00:05:58.191 --> 00:06:00.652 position:50% align:center
All right!

00:06:00.652 --> 00:06:02.487 position:50% align:center
Thank goodness.

00:06:08.660 --> 00:06:10.328 position:50% align:center
Gakuto!

00:06:10.328 --> 00:06:12.539 position:50% align:center
Great job on the turnover--

00:06:20.797 --> 00:06:24.592 position:50% align:center
Ever since I was young,
I was always the leader.

