What kind of attitude is that?

00:06:49.117 --> 00:06:51.119 position:50% align:center
Are you trying to be captain or something?

00:06:51.119 --> 00:06:52.328 position:50% align:center
What do you mean?

00:06:52.328 --> 00:06:54.664 position:50% align:center
