00:06:54.664 --> 00:06:56.791 position:50% align:center
That doesn't make sense.

00:06:56.791 --> 00:06:57.792 position:50% align:center
What?

00:06:57.792 --> 00:07:02.255 position:50% align:center
A person with a haughty attitude
wouldn't be fit to be captain.

00:07:03.631 --> 00:07:07.218 position:50% align:center
With those words, in a single moment,

00:07:07.218 --> 00:07:10.805 position:50% align:center
I realized I was never a true leader,

00:07:10.805 --> 00:07:15.643 position:50% align:center
and I became unsure
of what true camaraderie was.

00:07:15.643 --> 00:07:17.187 position:50% align:center
I see.

00:07:17.187 --> 00:07:22.275 position:50% align:center
The reason I played rugby
was so that I could lose against you.

00:07:22.275 --> 00:07:24.402 position:50% align:center
Ikuto, what's wrong?

00:07:24.402 --> 00:07:28.990 position:50% align:center
I was meant to lose against you,
dedicate myself to you, and grow...

00:07:28.990 --> 00:07:32.952 position:50% align:center
