00:09:13.261 --> 00:09:14.971 position:50% align:center line:10%
"10 Ibuki Ueoka"

00:09:15.638 --> 00:09:17.682 position:50% align:center
Kazutaka.

00:09:17.682 --> 00:09:19.809 position:50% align:center
Keep joining the scrum like this.

00:09:19.809 --> 00:09:21.686 position:50% align:center
We're changing our tactics.

00:09:23.146 --> 00:09:23.980 position:50% align:center
Now, now.

00:09:23.980 --> 00:09:26.358 position:50% align:center
Don't make such an unsatisfied face.

00:09:26.358 --> 00:09:29.235 position:50% align:center
The forwards on their side
are gaining a lot of momentum.

00:09:29.235 --> 00:09:32.655 position:50% align:center
